<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.1">
<l>viyamuṭai viṭaiyiṉa muṭaitara maṭamakaḷ</l>
<l>kuyamiṭai taṭavarai yakalama tuṭaiyavar</l>
<l>nayamuṭai naṭaiyaṉa miḷaiyavar naṭaipayil</l>
<l>kayamiṭai kaṇapura maṭikaḷta miṭamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of god, the one with a chest like a broad mountain</l>
<l rend="indent">where a simple girl</l>
<l>Pressed her breasts so that a herd of stout bulls was destroyed,</l>
<l>Is Kaṇṇapuram, crowded by pools where swans</l>
<l>With lovely gaits practice the gait of young girls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
